      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior Developer Position\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to reach out personally to express our gratitude for your interest in the Senior Developer position at our Austin-based company. We were truly impressed by your skills in system design and your seamless integration into our team culture.\n\nAfter careful consideration and thorough evaluation, we have decided to move forward with another candidate who possesses a bit more experience with our specific cloud stack. This decision was not easy, as we were genuinely impressed by your capabilities and potential.\n\nWe understand that this news may be disappointing, and we want to assure you that this does not reflect on your qualifications or your potential for success. We believe that you have a bright future ahead, and we hope that you will consider applying for future opportunities with us.\n\nThank you once again for your interest in our company and for your patience during the selection process. We wish you all the best in your future endeavors and hope that you will keep us in mind for any future openings that align with your skills and interests.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
